===============================================================================
ADDITIONAL NOTICES
===============================================================================

RESEARCH DATA AND FINDINGS

The annotated research corpus, trained model weights, and quantitative experimental
findings associated with this research program are not released under either license
above. They are withheld from public release pending peer-reviewed publication and
are subject to separate terms that will accompany the data release. See
docs/ip-and-disclosure-notice.md for the full data policy.

AUDIO CONTENT

No raw audio files are committed to this repository. The cinematic audio cues
that form the research corpus are original compositions by Bernard G. and are
not licensed for any use without explicit written permission.

INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY

This repository documents a research program that is pending intellectual property
review. The research methodology, annotation framework, and the Composer Gap study
design described in this repository represent original research contributions. Use
of the conceptual framework, annotation methodology, or study design for derivative
research or commercial applications requires attribution and, in commercial contexts,
prior written permission from the author.

See docs/ip-and-disclosure-notice.md for the complete IP and disclosure notice.

CITATION

If you use this repository, its methodology, schemas, or research documentation in
academic or professional work, please cite it. A machine-readable citation is
available in CITATION.cff. Human-readable guidance is in docs/citation-and-use-policy.md.

